SUMMARY:Neighborhood Wildflower Seed Planting (Swannanoa)
DESCRIPTION:Join NCWF Swannanoa Valley WILD! and Friends of Fox Creek Park alongside friends and neighbors to spread color and beauty as we spread thousands of beautiful and native wildflowers. We’ll spread over 15 species of wildflowers that we gathered this Fall plus a few others purchased from Sow True Seeds. We have enough seeds to dramatically boost the color of our park\, to feed many future generations of native bees and other pollinators and to share with anyone who would like to bring some of that native color home. And of course\, free food for all! \nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/neighborhood-wildflower-seed-planting-swannanoa/
CATEGORIES:Featured
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ncwf.org/wp-content/uploads/seeds.jpg
END:VEVENT
