SUMMARY:Pollinator Garden Cleanup (Marvin)
DESCRIPTION:Join NCWF Habitat Builders Chapter for an afternoon of maintenance in the pollinator garden at Marvin Efird Park. Volunteers are needed to assist with weeding\, pruning\, and general maintenance. \nPlease bring a hat and wear long pants. Bring your favorite gardening tools and a pair of gloves. Getting involved is a fantastic way to help with the Mayor’s Monarch Pledge!\n \nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/pollinator-garden-cleanup-marvin/
CATEGORIES:Featured
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ncwf.org/wp-content/uploads/PollinatorCleanup.jpg
