SUMMARY:Wildlife Benefit Banquet (Gastonia)
DESCRIPTION:Annually PAWS hosts an Oyster Roast and Wildlife Banquet to raise funds for Gaston County. We pride ourselves on our fundraisers and giving back to the Gaston County Community. All funds made from banquet are distributed to other 501C3 organizations that are operating in Gaston County and the Piedmont. PAWS is focused on supporting our local community. \nEvent info: \nAdmission ticket to the Annual Wildlife Banquet includes Dinner (BBQ\, Chicken and Oyster Roast) and Drinks. Live Auction and Raffles are not included in ticket purchase and sold separately at the event. The Live Auction and Raffles raise funds for the Gaston County Community\, Wildlife Conservation and Education throughout the Gaston County and the Piedmont. \nCouple Sponsors (2 admission tickets\, 1 Sponsor Raffle Entry)\, Table Sponsors (8 individual tickets\, 4 Sponsor Raffle Entries) and Pre-Banquet Raffle tickets may be purchased by emailing info@gastonpaws.comor by contacting 704-864-0441. \nThank you for your continued support to Gaston County PAWS and we look forward to seeing you at Wood Duck Farm on March 14\, 2026 @ 6:00 PM. \nLEARN MORE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/wildlife-benefit-banquet-gastonia/
CATEGORIES:Featured
END:VEVENT
