SUMMARY:Wildlife Trivia (Matthews)
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Wildlife Trivia at 6 Grogs Game Bar in Matthews! Enjoy free snacks while you sip a frosty beverage and test your knowledge against other Nature Nerds! Win prizes and\, more importantly\, BRAGGING RIGHTS! Learn about the wildlife all around us while having fun with like-minded folks! Proceeds from the evening support the NCWF Habitat and Wildlife Keepers Chapter and wildlife work in the Matthews area! \nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/wildlife-trivia-matthews-3/
CATEGORIES:Featured
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ncwf.org/wp-content/uploads/HAWKTRIVIA6Grogs-3.jpg
END:VEVENT
