SUMMARY:Beech Bluff Bash (Willow Spring)
DESCRIPTION:Join NCWF South Wake Conservationists Chapter in celebrating nature at Wake County’s newest park! SWC is seeking volunteers to assist with the chapter’s exhibit\, helping setup or break down and engaging with both kids and adults during the event. No experiece is necessary–all instructions and supplies will be provided. This year’s booth theme is Wildlife Habitat. Come for the first shift\, the second shift\, or both then enjoy exploring this beautiful 300 acre park! \nREGISTER HERE
